data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of East New York! This captivating 2 Family property at 753 New Jersey Avenue is a true gem that offers an incredible opportunity for comfortable and versatile living.  Upon entering, you will be greeted by a galley kitchen, boasting an abundance of cabinets, counter space, and storage. Imagine preparing delicious meals while enjoying the natural light that floods this space. The unique features of this property include a front porch and a back porch, allowing you to relax and soak in the surrounding beauty.  Inside, you will find built-in wall units that add charm and character to the home. The finished basement, complete with an egress to the front and backyard, provides versatility and additional living space. You will also appreciate the convenience of a front sunroom and backyard mudroom, offering flexibility and functionality for your everyday needs. The skylight allows natural light to illuminate the interior, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. With East and West exposure, this property enjoys an abundance of natural light throughout the day.   But the allure of this property doesn't stop there. Venture outside to discover an impressive outdoor space that is perfect for relaxing and entertaining. Imagine hosting summer barbecues, gardening, or simply enjoying a peaceful moment in your own private retreat.  Living in the East New York neighborhood has never been more enticing. Enjoy the convenience of nearby attractions, top-rated schools, and a plethora of restaurants that cater to every culinary craving. Plus, with easy access to public transportation, commuting to work or exploring the vibrant city has never been easier.  Excellent opportunity to make a house into your very own custom home. This exceptional property is within reach. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or looking for an investment opportunity, this listing is a must-see. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your forever home! Schedule a viewing today. Your dream home awaits!  This property will be sold vacant. As-is. VS photos added.
